<L>__{2: exterior oakland bridge. san francisco bay. dusk.}
<A>__{high above the golden gate. too high for specifics. but there is something down there of interest to the camera. descending with the music it seems to isolate a particular car. too many and too distant to know which it is. but the camera is follow ing and already a mile up the 101 interstate travelling north. maybe via a dissolve. and maybe not. but red and white either way as the headlights are coming on. the camera is closing on the highway. and a car has definitely been selected. there is nothing much of interest about it. it's a blue mercedes sedan. mussorgsky will choreograph the pace of these cuts. the first puts the frame directly in front of the car. in a few moments its brights snap up. and titles continue in a dazzle of light.}
